<para id="element-20">The MI integral is then expressed by suitably replacing "dm" term by density term in the integral expression. This approach to integration using elemental mass assumes that mass distribution is uniform. </para>
</section>

<section id="section-2">
<title> Evaluation of moment of inertia </title>

<para id="element-21">In this section, we shall determine MI of known geometric bodies about the axis of its symmetry. </para>

